abstract: Andrea Petkovic beats Carina Witthoft in first round of Bank of the West Classic; other tennis results noted.
lead_paragraph: Sixth-seeded Andrea Petkovic beat Carina Witthöft in the first round of the Bank of the West Classic in Stanford, Calif.
